# Stage 05 — verification (L2)

Technical audit of what was delivered in stage 04. No new code. Verifies that outputs declared in `plan.md` and `wave-plan.md` exist in the FS, runs global CI locally (or consults status), and does a sample-check of 3 random ADRs — verifies they were cited in ≥1 task report. CI failure becomes `BLOCKED_ERROR` (not a stop point — verification is deterministic like the wave-planner).

