## v3.3.0 references applicable to this stage

- **Diagnose protocol fallback (`_references/runtime/diagnose-protocol.md`):**
  when CI fails OR coverage fails, activate 6-phase diagnose instead of trying
  ad-hoc fix. Phase 1 (build feedback loop) is THE skill — without a
  reproducible loop, do not advance. Hypotheses 3-5 ranked falsifiable. Tag debug
  logs with `[DEBUG-xxxx]` for cleanup grep at the end.
- **Additional output:** `output/diagnose-report.md` with repro evidence,
  ranked hypotheses, root cause, fix, regression test (path).
- **HITL loop (`_config/hitl-loop.template.sh`):** bash template for bugs
  that require human manual interaction. Customize `REPRO_STEPS`,
  `OBSERVE_CMD`, `PASS_PATTERN`.
